(21, 11, 7, '', '', 0, 'ssc-notified-for-stenographer-grade', 'SSC Notified for Stenographer Grade and Grade Ex', '<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify;">Staff Selection Commission invited application for recruitment to the post of Stenographer Grade &lsquo;C&rsquo; and Grade &lsquo;D&rsquo;. The candidates eligible for the post can apply through prescribed format before 26 October 2013.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><span style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important; text-decoration: underline;">Important Date</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none inside; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 13px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">