(24, 11, 7, '', '', 0, 'accountant-junior-accountant-vacancies', 'Accountant, Junior Accountant Vacancies in Power Sector in Rajas', '<p style="color: rgb(109, 109, 107); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;">Power sector companies of Rajasthan invites online applications from eligible candidates for the post of Accountant and Junior Accountant. 55 Accountant and 492 Jr Accountant vacancies to be filled in different power companies in Rajasthan.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; line-height: 28px; font-family: HelveticaCondensedMedium; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(109, 109, 107);">Power Sector Companies of Rajasthan</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul style="color: rgb(109, 109, 107); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;">\r\n	<li>Rajasthan Rajya Vidyut Prasasan Nigam Ltd (RVPNL)</li>\r\n	<li>Rajasthan Rajya Vidyut Utpadan Nigam Ltd (RVUNL)</li>\r\n	<li>Jaipur Vidyut Vitran Nigam Ltd (JVVNL)</li>\r\n	<li>Ajmer Vidyut Vitran Nigam Ltd (AVVNL)</li>\r\n	<li>Jodhpur Vidhyut Vitran Nigam Ltd (Jd.VVNL)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; line-height: 30px; font-family: HelveticaCondensedMedium; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(109, 109, 107);">Accountant and Junior Accountant Vacancies in Rajasthan Power Sector Companies</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="color: rgb(109, 109, 107); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;"><strong>Vacancies Details:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="1" style="color: rgb(109, 109, 107); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;" width="200">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Name of Company</strong></td>\r\n			<td colspan="2">\r\n			<table border="1">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td colspan="2"><strong>Name of Posts</strong></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td><strong>Accountant</strong></td>\r\n						<td><strong>Junior Accountant</strong></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>RVPNL</td>\